## Usage

```javascript
import SimpleSlider from 'simple-reactjs-slider';

export default () => (
  //slider-wrap need set width and height
  <div id='slider-wrap'>
    <SimpleSlider min={0} max={100} vertical onChange={(e)=>{}}  defaultValue={15} />
  </div>
);
```
### demo
<img height='200px' src="data:image/png;base64,">

### Slider

| Name         | Type    | Default | Description |
| ------------ | ------- | ------- | ----------- |
| defaultValue | number | `0` | Set initial value of slider. |
| min | number | `0` | Set minimum value of slider. |
| max | number | `0` | Set maximum value of slider. |
| vertical | boolean | `false` | if false then horizontal slider. |
